<div class="max-w-xs sm:max-w-xl md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16">
  <section class="prose prose-sm sm:prose md:prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 sm:mb-10 md:mb-12">
    <p>
      The founding purpose of Ruby Australia is to further the use and adoption of the Ruby programming language in Australia,
      and to support and encourage a vibrant community around the language and related technologies.
    </p>

    <p>
      We are very lucky to have many companies who have provided sponsorship over the years to help us achieve these goals,
      particularly through our <a href="/#in-person" class="text-ruby-red hover:text-red-700 transition-colors">regular events</a>: RubyConf AU, Rails Camp, ongoing city meetups,
      and Rails Girls. Their sponsorship support combined with the massive efforts of our volunteer organisers have created
      world-class conferences and gatherings.
    </p>

    <p>If you are interested in becoming a Ruby AU sponsor, please download our current Sponsorship Prospectus:</p>

    <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4 sm:pl-6">
      <li>
        <%= link_to "2025 Sponsorship - Prospectus [PDF]", "/files/pdfs/RubyAU-Sponsorship-Prospectus-2025.pdf",
                    class: "text-ruby-red hover:text-red-700 transition-colors inline-flex items-center" %>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= link_to "2025 Sponsorship - Executive Summary [PDF]", "/files/pdfs/RubyAU-Sponsorship-Prospectus-2025-Exec-Summary.pdf",
                    class: "text-ruby-red hover:text-red-700 transition-colors inline-flex items-center" %>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      You should also feel free to contact our sponsorship representatives via email:
      <%= mail_to "sponsorship@ruby.org.au", class: "text-ruby-red hover:text-red-700 transition-colors font-medium" %>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="sponsors" class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 sm:pt-10 md:pt-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 sm:mb-10 md:mb-12 text-center sm:text-left">
      Our Sponsors
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-12 sm:space-y-16 md:space-y-20">
      <% @sponsors.group_by { |sponsor| sponsor['tier'] }.each do |tier, sponsors| %>
        <div class="sponsor-tier">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-6 sm:mb-8 pb-2 border-b border-gray-200">
            <%= tier %> Sponsors
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-12">
            <% sponsors.each do |sponsor| %>
              <div class="sponsor-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 sm:p-8">
                <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-ruby-red mb-4">
                  <%= link_to sponsor['name'], sponsor['url'],
                              class: "hover:text-red-700 transition-colors" %>
                </h4>
                <div class="sponsor-logos flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center justify-center sm:justify-start mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                  <% sponsor['images'].each do |image| %>
                    <%= link_to sponsor['url'], class: "block" do %>
                      <%= vite_image_tag "images/sponsors/#{image}",
                                         class: "max-h-16 sm:max-h-20 md:max-h-24 w-auto object-contain" %>
                    <% end %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
                <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none">
                  <%= markdown_to_html sponsor['bio'] %>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
